229
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:59,840
Now what happens then when you introduce technology into production?

230
00:21:59,840 --> 00:22:04,840
You produce enormous quantities of goods by technological methods.

231
00:22:04,840 --> 00:22:09,560
But at the same time you put people out of work.

232
00:22:09,560 --> 00:22:14,480
You can say oh but it always creates more jobs, there will always be more jobs, yes.

233
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:18,040
But lots of them will be futile jobs.

234
00:22:18,040 --> 00:22:24,560
They will be jobs making every kind of frippery and unnecessary contraption.

235
00:22:24,560 --> 00:22:28,120
And one will also at the same time have to beguile the public into feeling that they

236
00:22:28,120 --> 00:22:33,480
need and want these completely unnecessary things that aren't even beautiful.

