00:24:17,560 --> 00:24:21,280
the manufacturer and say you can't own and run this factory anymore, it is owned by the

256
00:24:21,280 --> 00:24:22,280
government.

257
00:24:22,280 --> 00:24:29,480
It is only saying that the government or the people have to be responsible for issuing

258
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:37,840
to themselves sufficient credit to circulate the goods they are producing and have to balance

259
00:24:37,840 --> 00:24:45,600
the measuring standard of money with the gross national product.

260
00:24:45,600 --> 00:24:49,560
That means that taxation is obsolete, completely obsolete.

261
00:24:49,560 --> 00:24:55,520
We ought to go the other way, fear bold points out, that every individual should be assured

